# M16.135: /dev/stat + /dev/mounts + /dev/diskstats system-introspection
# trio. Their FD_*_MARK constants live IN the dev*.ad files themselves
# (rather than kernel/sched/core.ad) because the parallel-agent fence
# for this commit forbids touching core.ad. Adder's flat-merge symbol
# model means the imported constants land in the same single image .bss
# as core.ad's existing markers — they're indistinguishable to the
# codegen, just colocated with their dispatch arms.
